<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Grade Feedback from {{instructorName}}</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
<table style="border: 0; width: 100%;">
  <tr style="background: #f2f2f2;">
    <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #333;">
      {{courseName}}
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 20px; font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
      <p>Dear {{studentName}},</p>
      <p>Your grade for the {{typeName}} "{{name}}" is now available. Below is the detailed feedback
        from {{instructorName}}:</p>
      <blockquote style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #00838f; background-color: #fafafa;">
        {{feedback}}
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #ff9800; background-color: #fafafa;">
        <strong>Grade: {{grade}} / {{maxGrade}}</strong>
      </blockquote>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
      <a href="{{gradePortalUrl}}"
         style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #4caf50; border-radius: 5px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;">
        View Your Complete Grade Here
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 20px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; color: #999;">
      If you have any questions, feel free to contact {{instructorEmail}}.
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>

</html>
